'''薩爾瓦多醫院'''（{{lang-es|Hospital El Salvador}}）是位於[[薩爾瓦多|薩爾瓦多]]首都[[聖薩爾瓦多|聖薩爾瓦多]]的大型醫院，亦是[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]最大的醫療機構，建於2020年3－6月，由原{{tsl|es|Centro Internacional de Ferias y Convenciones|國際會展中心 (薩爾瓦多)|國際會展中心}}改建而成，用以應對{{tsl|en|COVID-19 pandemic in El Salvador|2019冠狀病毒病薩爾瓦多疫情|薩爾瓦多}}的[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]，該院專門收治感染[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]的患者。薩爾瓦多醫院原先僅計畫臨時性興建，但其於2020年6月宣布將成為永久性醫院，該院在興建的第一期工程引進了400張病床，而病床總數預計在第三期工程完工後增加到2,000張。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Fachada_Hospital_El_Salvador.jpg|left]]
2020年3月14日，[[薩爾瓦多總統|薩爾瓦多總統]][[納伊布·布格磊|納伊布·布格磊]]宣布將在該國的{{tsl|es|Centro Internacional de Ferias y Convenciones|國際會展中心 (薩爾瓦多)|國際會展中心}}內建造一座臨時醫院<ref>{{cite news|work=El Diario de Hoy|url=https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/coronavirus-cifco-hospital-especializado/695920/2020/|date=2020-03-14|accessdate=2020-06-29|first=Xiomara|last=Alfaro|title=Cifco será el primer hospital especializado para atender a pacientes con coronavirus, informa Gobierno|trans-title=CIFCO will be the first specialized hospital to treat coronavirus patients, according to the Government|language=es|archive-date=2020-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625212511/https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/coronavirus-cifco-hospital-especializado/695920/2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當時薩爾瓦多境內還未通報任何[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]病例，但布格磊預測該國的醫療體系很可能在疫情爆發後「崩潰」（collapse）。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://diario.elmundo.sv/invertiran-70-millones-en-cifco-para-convertilo-en-hospital/|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2020-03-16|work=El Mundo|first=Iliana|last=Cornejo|title=Invertirán $70 millones en Cifco para convertirlo en hospital|language=es|trans-title=$70 million to be invested in CIFCO to convert it to a hospital|archive-date=2020-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329030338/https://diario.elmundo.sv/invertiran-70-millones-en-cifco-para-convertilo-en-hospital/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|es|Corte de Cuentas de El Salvador|薩爾瓦多會計法院}}於同年4月建議將新醫院建設成永久醫院，法院院長則提議將原來的國際會展中心移至他處。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.eleconomista.net/actualidad/Corte-de-Cuentas-de-El-Salvador-recomienda-que-hospital-en-CIFCO-sea-permanente-20200407-0012.html|work=El Economista|first=Mariana|last=Arévalo|date=2020-04-07|accessdate=2020-06-29|title=Corte de Cuentas de El Salvador recomienda que hospital en CIFCO sea permanente|trans-title=Transparency Court of El Salvador recommends that CIFCO hospital be permanent|language=es|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630022756/https://www.eleconomista.net/actualidad/Corte-de-Cuentas-de-El-Salvador-recomienda-que-hospital-en-CIFCO-sea-permanente-20200407-0012.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>醫院施工期間，施工人員被分配成三個工作班次以加快工程進度。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://ultimahora.sv/esta-semana-abriran-hospitales-temporales-para-pacientes-de-coronavirus-en-tecoluca-y-jiquilisco/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Última Hora|date=2020-04-08|title=Esta semana abrirán hospitales temporales para pacientes de coronavirus en Tecoluca y Jiquilisco|language=es|trans-title=This week temporary hospitals for coronavirus patients will open in Tecoluca and Jiquilisco|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629181423/https://ultimahora.sv/esta-semana-abriran-hospitales-temporales-para-pacientes-de-coronavirus-en-tecoluca-y-jiquilisco/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年5月，{{tsl|es|Ministerio de Obras Públicas y Transporte de El Salvador|公共工程和運輸部 (薩爾瓦多)|薩爾瓦多公共工程和運輸部}}的兩名工人對病毒的檢測呈現陽性，興建工程因而暫停。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://focostv.com/personal-del-mop-que-trabaja-en-construccion-del-hospital-del-cifco-da-positivo-por-covid-19/|date=2020-05-05|first=David|last=Bernal|work=Focos TV|title=Personal del MOP que trabaja en construcción del Hospital del CIFCO da positivo por Covid-19|trans-title=MOP personnel working on construction of the CIFCO Hospital test positive for COVID-19|accessdate=2020-06-29|language=es|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701134829/https://focostv.com/personal-del-mop-que-trabaja-en-construccion-del-hospital-del-cifco-da-positivo-por-covid-19/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年6月22日，總統納伊布·布格磊為醫院主持了第一期工程的落成典禮{{r|lanotta}}，同時宣布醫院因投資鉅額而將成為永久改建{{r|efe}}，並將其命名為「薩爾瓦多醫院」，醫院在隔日正式啟用。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://elsalvadorgram.com/2020/06/nayib-bukele-anuncia-que-hospital-de-cifco-se-llamara-hospital-el-salvador-este-lugar-nos-representa-asegura/|date=2020-06-21|title=Nayib Bukele anuncia que hospital de CIFCO se llamará ‘Hospital El Salvador’: "Este lugar nos representa", asegura|trans-title=Nayib Bukele announces that CIFCO hospital will be known as 'Hospital El Salvador': "This place represents us," he assures|language=es|work=ElSalvadorgram|accessdate=2020-06-29|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702223021/https://elsalvadorgram.com/2020/06/nayib-bukele-anuncia-que-hospital-de-cifco-se-llamara-hospital-el-salvador-este-lugar-nos-representa-asegura/|dead-url=no}}</ref>落成典禮不對外向[[記者|記者]]開放，政府官員亦多次拒絕[[攝影師|攝影師]]進入典禮現場。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/cifco-coronavirus-hospital-inauguracion-primera-fase/725830/2020/|work=El Diario de Hoy|first1=R|last=Tejada|first2=Xiomara|last2=Alfaro|date=2020-06-21|title=Gobierno impide acceso a la prensa durante inauguración de primera fase de hospital Cifco|trans-title=Government impedes access to press during inauguration of first phase of CIFCO hospital|language=es|accessdate=2020-06-29|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702162716/https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/cifco-coronavirus-hospital-inauguracion-primera-fase/725830/2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>整座醫院耗資7,500萬[[美元|美元]]，其中2,500萬美元用於改建國際會展中心（第一期工程）{{r|comercio}}，占地{{convert|36000|m2|ft2}}，設有血庫、[[太平間|太平間]]和患者監控中心等設施{{r|comercio}}，薩爾瓦多政府也在開院同時開始招聘醫療及行政人員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/hospital-el-salvador-plazas-empleos-covid-19/727609/2020/|work=El Diario de Hoy|accessdate=2020-06-26|date=2020-06-21|title=Estas son las plazas vacantes en el nuevo Hospital El Salvador|author=Vanessa Jurado|language=es|trans-title=These are the vacant positions in the new Hospital El Salvador|archive-date=2020-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628165229/https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/hospital-el-salvador-plazas-empleos-covid-19/727609/2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2019冠狀病毒病疫情爆發前，薩爾瓦多全國有30張[[加護病房|加護病床]]（ICU），而薩爾瓦多醫院第一期工程完成後將增加至157張。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.contrapunto.com.sv/politica/gobierno/minsal-celebra-inauguracion-de-hospital-el-salvador/14236|work=Contrapunto|date=2020-06-22|title=MINSAL celebra inauguración de Hospital El Salvador|accessdate=2020-06-29|language=es|trans-title=MINSAL [Health Ministry] celebrates inauguration of Hospital El Salvador|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630042515/https://www.contrapunto.com.sv/politica/gobierno/minsal-celebra-inauguracion-de-hospital-el-salvador/14236|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{tsl|en|University of El Salvador|薩爾瓦多大學}}於醫院落成後發布了一份新聞稿，呼籲薩爾瓦多醫院最終轉型為該大學的[[醫學院|醫學院]]。<ref>{{Cite news|agency=Associated Press|work=Houston Chronicle|url=https://www.chron.com/news/article/El-Salvador-pone-a-funcionar-hospital-para-15364502.php|title=El Salvador pone a funcionar hospital para COVID-19|date=2020-06-24|accessdate=2020-06-29|trans-title=El Salvador puts into operation COVID-19 hospital|language=es|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627115052/https://www.chron.com/news/article/El-Salvador-pone-a-funcionar-hospital-para-15364502.php|archive-date=2020-06-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>而會計法院留意到自醫院啟用後，{{tsl|es|Ministerio de Salud (El Salvador)|衛生部 (薩爾瓦多)|薩爾瓦多衛生部}}都未曾允許審計人員和記者進入太平間等重要區域以檢查改建後的會展中心是否具備醫院必要的基礎設備。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.eleconomista.net/actualidad/El-Salvador-La-inconclusa-transformacion-del-CIFCO-en-un-hospital-20200716-0001.html|work=El Economista|language=es|first=Edwin|last=Segura|title=El Salvador: La inconclusa transformación del CIFCO en un hospital|trans-title=El Salvador: The incomplete transformation of CIFCO into a hospital|date=2020-07-16|accessdate=2020-07-25|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726031201/https://www.eleconomista.net/actualidad/El-Salvador-La-inconclusa-transformacion-del-CIFCO-en-un-hospital-20200716-0001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年3月，會計法院指出醫院的施工過程存在63處異常，包括缺乏[[汙水處理|汙水處理]]設施等。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Velásquez |first=Eugenia |date=2021-03-18 |title=Corte de Cuentas halla 63 anomalías en edificación del Hospital El Salvador |language=es |trans-title=Transparency Court finds 63 anomalies in construction of Hospital El Salvador |work=El Salvador |url=https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/corte-de-cuentas-hace-63-reparos-informe-construccion-hospital-el-salvador/818443/2021/ |access-date=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2021-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330161017/https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/corte-de-cuentas-hace-63-reparos-informe-construccion-hospital-el-salvador/818443/2021/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

最後階段的第三期工程由於需興建全新的建築，因此於2020年10月的工程進較為緩慢，比計畫的時間延遲了2個月，該國政府預計第三期建築將於2021年1月投入使用。<ref name="paredes">{{Cite news |last=Velásquez |first=Eugenia |date=2020-10-22 |title=Tras lento avance en tercera fase del Hospital El Salvador, ministro de Obras Públicas dice comenzarán a levantar paredes |language=es |work=elsalvador |url=https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/ministro-obras-publicas-construccion-tercera-fase-hospital-elsalvador/767319/2020/ |access-date=2020-11-20 |trans-title=After slow progress on third phase of Hospital El Salvador, Minister of Public Works says they will start to raise walls |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125135409/https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/ministro-obras-publicas-construccion-tercera-fase-hospital-elsalvador/767319/2020/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>直至2021年3<ref name="sincon">{{Cite news |date=2021-03-07 |title=Tercera fase del Hospital El Salvador sin concluir |language=es-ES |trans-title=Third phase of Hospital El Salvador unfinished |work=YSUCA |url=http://ysuca.org.sv/2021/03/07/tercera-fase-del-hospital-el-salvador-sin-concluir/ |access-date=2021-08-28 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308233109/http://ysuca.org.sv/2021/03/07/tercera-fase-del-hospital-el-salvador-sin-concluir/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、4月初時該國公共工程和運輸部長宣稱已完工，惟仍有工人進出醫院。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Hernández |first=William |date=2021-04-06 |title=Sin destino el uso del hospital construido en parqueo del Cifco |language=es |trans-title=Undefined, the use of the hospital built in the Cifco parking lot |work=El Salvador |url=https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/hospital-el-salvador-cifco-concluido/824520/2021/ |access-date=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424222347/https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/hospital-el-salvador-cifco-concluido/824520/2021/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>第三期建築最終於同年4月13日啟用，用於大規模接種[[2019冠状病毒病疫苗|疫苗]]。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Villeda |first=Jaqueline |date=2021-04-12 |title=Tercera fase de Hospital El Salvador sería centro de vacunación |language=es |trans-title=Third phase of Hospital El Salvador to be vaccination center |work=El Mundo |url=https://diario.elmundo.sv/tercera-fase-de-hospital-el-salvador-seria-centro-de-vacunacion/ |access-date=2021-06-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413033042/https://diario.elmundo.sv/tercera-fase-de-hospital-el-salvador-seria-centro-de-vacunacion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 設備 ==
薩爾瓦多醫院的第一期工程完工後有400張病床，其中包括105張[[加護病房|加護病床]]和295普通病床，醫院計畫在第三期工程完工後將病床數增加至2,000<ref name="comercio">{{cite news|url=https://www.elcomercio.com/actualidad/bukele-hospital-uci-covid-salvador.html|title=Nayib Bukele inaugura en El Salvador primera fase del ‘mejor hospital de Latinoamérica’ exclusivo para covid-19|language=es|trans-title=Nayib Bukele opens in El Salvador the first phase of the "best hospital in Latin America" exclusively for COVID-19|agency=AFP|work=El Comercio|date=2020-06-24|accessdate=2020-06-28|archive-date=2020-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626233241/https://www.elcomercio.com/actualidad/bukele-hospital-uci-covid-salvador.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中包含1,083張加護病床。{{r|lanotta}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.europapress.es/internacional/noticia-salvador-inaugura-hospital-solo-pacientes-covid-19-capacidad-2000-camas-20200622041616.html|work=Europa Press|location=Madrid|date=2020-06-22|accessdate=2020-06-29|title=El Salvador inaugura un hospital solo para pacientes de la COVID-19 con una capacidad de 2.000 camas|language=es|trans-title=El Salvador opens a hospital exclusively for COVID-19 patients with a capacity of 2,000 beds|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630012606/https://www.europapress.es/internacional/noticia-salvador-inaugura-hospital-solo-pacientes-covid-19-capacidad-2000-camas-20200622041616.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二和第三期工程預計原於2020年8月完工，但三期工程因招標問題而延誤2個月<ref name="efe">{{cite news|url=https://www.efe.com/efe/america/sociedad/el-salvador-inaugura-primera-fase-de-un-hospital-exclusivo-para-la-covid-19/20000013-4277484|work=EFE|date=2020-06-22|title=El Salvador inaugura primera fase de un hospital exclusivo para la COVID-19|language=es|trans-title=El Salvador inaugurates first phase of a hospital exclusively for COVID-19|accessdate=2020-06-28|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630221215/https://www.efe.com/efe/america/sociedad/el-salvador-inaugura-primera-fase-de-un-hospital-exclusivo-para-la-covid-19/20000013-4277484|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Edificio anexo a hospital CIFCO suma dos meses de atraso en construcción|url=https://www.laprensagrafica.com/elsalvador/Edificio-anexo-a-hospital-CIFCO-suma-dos-meses-de-atraso-en-construccion-20200821-0083.html|author=Cecilia Fuentes|date=2020-08-22|accessdate=2020-09-17|work=La Prensa Gráfica|language=es|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902215849/https://www.laprensagrafica.com/elsalvador/Edificio-anexo-a-hospital-CIFCO-suma-dos-meses-de-atraso-en-construccion-20200821-0083.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其將在原國際會展中心停車場興建一座三層樓建築。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.lapagina.com.sv/nacionales/hospital-el-salvador-da-de-alta-a-los-primeros-5-pacientes-que-fueron-ingresados-esta-semana/|accessdate=2020-06-28|date=2020-06-27|work=La Página|first=Julio|last=Villarán|title=Hospital El Salvador da de alta a los primeros 5 pacientes que fueron ingresados esta semana|language=es|trans-title=Hospital El Salvador discharges first 5 patients admitted this week|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629070658/https://www.lapagina.com.sv/nacionales/hospital-el-salvador-da-de-alta-a-los-primeros-5-pacientes-que-fueron-ingresados-esta-semana/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

薩爾瓦多境內所有在其他醫院治療的2019冠狀病毒病病例均會被轉院至薩爾瓦多醫院，以舒緩該國的醫療衛生體系。{{r|lanotta}}但薩爾瓦多醫學界協會（Colegio Médico Milton Brizuela）2020年7月的一份報告顯示，薩爾瓦多醫院僅使用了其25％的容納空間。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://ysuca.org.sv/2020/07/20/colegio-medico-hospital-el-salvador-ha-usado-solo-el-25-de-su-capacidad/|work=YSUCA|title=Colegio Médico: Hospital El Salvador ha usado solo el 25% de su capacidad|trans-title=Medical College: Hospital El Salvador has only used 25% of its capacity|language=es|date=2020-07-20|accessdate=2020-07-25|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726031338/http://ysuca.org.sv/2020/07/20/colegio-medico-hospital-el-salvador-ha-usado-solo-el-25-de-su-capacidad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>協會主席於同年12月進一步警告，由於醫院的三期工程尚未完工，而院內已住滿冠狀病毒病患者，醫療系統具有崩潰風險。<ref>{{Cite news |date=2020-12-30 |title=Los hospitales se están saturando de pacientes con COVID-19, sin que el Hospital El Salvador esté terminado |language=es |trans-title=The hospitals are filling up with COVID-19 patients as the Hospital El Salvador is still unfinished |work=YSUCA |url=http://ysuca.org.sv/2020/12/30/los-hospitales-se-estan-saturando-de-pacientes-con-covid-19-sin-que-el-hospital-el-salvador-este-terminado/ |access-date=2021-01-02 |archive-date=2020-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230234827/http://ysuca.org.sv/2020/12/30/los-hospitales-se-estan-saturando-de-pacientes-con-covid-19-sin-que-el-hospital-el-salvador-este-terminado/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 爭議 ==
2020年12月發表於醫學期刊《[[刺胳針|刺胳針]]》的文章針對薩爾瓦多醫院作出介紹，但獨立資訊網站《放大镜下看健康》（''Salud con Lupa''）揭露文章的意見內容是由薩爾瓦多政府出資撰寫。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Romero |first=Cecibel |date=2021-02-11 |title=Hospital El Salvador costea publicación de artículos en revistas internacionales |language=es |trans-title=Hospital El Salvador foots the bill for publication of articles in international journals |work=Salud con Lupa |url=https://saludconlupa.com/noticias/hospital-el-salvador-costea-publicacion-de-articulos-en-revistas-internacionales/ |access-date=2021-02-16 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213040437/https://saludconlupa.com/noticias/hospital-el-salvador-costea-publicacion-de-articulos-en-revistas-internacionales/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2021年4月，一封致《刺胳針》的公開信表明對醫院設計上的質疑。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Amaral |first=Arevalo |last2=Wenham |first2=Clare |date=2021-04-01 |title=Hospital El Salvador: broader questions remain |url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/langlo/article/PIIS2214-109X(21)00048-6/abstract |journal=The Lancet Global Health |language=en |volume=9 |issue=4 |pages=e406 |doi=10.1016/S2214-109X(21)00048-6 |issn=2214-109X |pmc=7963446 |pmid=33647236 |access-date=2022-02-20 |archive-date=2022-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220161928/https://www.thelancet.com/journals/langlo/article/PIIS2214-109X(21)00048-6/fulltext |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年11月，醫院的建築師喬納森·蒙松（Jonathan Monzón）被發現未取得其建築學士學位。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Beltrán Luna |first=Jorge |date=2021-11-14 |title=Autor de diseño de hospital El Salvador no aparece en registros de arquitectos de Ministerio de Vivienda |language=es |trans-title=Designer of Hospital El Salvador building does not appear on registry of architects of the Housing Ministry |work=El Diario de Hoy |url=https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/autor-diseno-hospital-el-salvador-no-aparece-registros-arquitectos/900317/2021/ |access-date=2021-11-21 |archive-date=2021-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121223244/https://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/nacional/autor-diseno-hospital-el-salvador-no-aparece-registros-arquitectos/900317/2021/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

